strings: <voice_0x01001229><se_high>Jessica: I-It's not possible... N-No human...could match the power...of the sceptre...!
<voice_0x0100122A><se_high>Jessica: ...You won't...get away with this...!
<voice_0x0100122B><se_high>Jessica: Now...you'll see...the true...power...of this sceptre! Already it...has ended the bloodlines...of four of the sages!

<voice_0x0100122C><se_high>Jessica: ...This town will burn!
And every one of you will perish!

<voice_0x0100122D><se_low>Dominico: Get out of the way!
Move! Move!

<voice_0x0100122E><se_low>Dominico: Ha ha ha ha hah!
Just in the nick of time!
The barrier is ready!
<voice_0x0100122F><se_low>Dominico: You villainous fiend! Take my life, would you!? Well you'll have to break through my barrier first! Alakazam!
<voice_0x01001230><se_low>Dominico: Ah ha ha ha hah! Behold, I am a mastermind!
<voice_0x01001231><se_low>Dominico: Well done! You did a fine job of keeping her at bay until I was ready!
<voice_0x01001232><se_low>Dominico: I must reward you! You may have the honour of finishing her off! Do you accept?

<voice_0x01001233><se_low>Dominico: Good! Then strike her down!
May she never meddle in my affairs again!
<voice_0x01001234><se_low>King Trode: Waaait! Have you gone completely doolally!?
<voice_0x01001235><se_low>Yangus: COR BLIMEY!
<voice_0x01001236><se_low>Dominico: Who is this strange creature? A friend of yours? Hm... It seems there's more to this situation than meets the eye.
<voice_0x01001237><se_low>Dominico: Tell me what's going on!
<voice_0x01001238><se_low>Dominico: What!? Why on earth not? Explain yourself!
<Cap><leader> explains the situation to Dominico.
<voice_0x01001239><se_low>Dominico: Well, well! So this girl is a friend of yours?
<voice_0x0100123A><se_low>Dominico: And she's been under some kind of curse ever since you defeated Dhoulmagus?

<voice_0x0100123B><se_low>Dominico: Hmph! Hardly a good excuse!
But I don't care any more.
The girl is yours to do with as you please!
<voice_0x0100123C><se_low>Dominico: Consider it a reward for attempting to protect my life.
<voice_0x0100123D><se_low>Dominico: There won't be any financial reward, of course! Haa ha ha ha hah!
<voice_0x0100123E><se_low>Dominico: Wait! Where's Sir Leopold?
<voice_0x0100123F><se_low>Dominico: He's gone! He must have been scared off by all the disturbance!
<voice_0x01001240><se_low>Dominico: David! Go and find Sir Leopold at once!
<voice_0x01001241><se_def>David: Y-Yes, Master!

<center>The party carries the unconscious Jessica
<center>to the inn.

<center>She appears to be having some kind of
<center>dream from which she cannot wake up.
